---
title: Lemongrass Tofu Coconut Curry with Veggies
description: Some flavour combinations are classics for good reason—lemongrass and coconut milk is one of them! Carrots further enhance the sweetness of these ingredients, and zesty cilantro rice brings all the tasty elements together. Warm flatbreads seal the deal.
